{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f6a89abd2d","title":"九月战役的兵力部署和粮弹储备","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"47ced6b5e8","index":0,"year":1951,"month":8,"day":1,"articleId":"f6a89abd2d"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji30","name":"毛泽东全集第30卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/30-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji30":{"comments":[{"id":"503e0ad3c2","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"f6a89abd2d","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"德怀，即彭德怀，当时任中国人民志愿军司令员兼政治委员。"},{"id":"d33169f972","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"f6a89abd2d","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"高，指高岗，当时任东北军区司令员兼政治委员。"},{"id":"59a52a83c5","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"f6a89abd2d","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"中国人民志愿军原拟定1951年9月对敌实施战役反击。后来，根据中共中央军委指示，决定推退执行战役反击计划（只加紧准备而不发动），准备对故实施战术反击。"}],"contents":[{"id":"332620964b","type":"title","text":"九月战役的兵力部署和粮弹储备","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"f6a89abd2d"},{"id":"503e0ad3c2","type":"paragraph","text":"德怀同志，并告高","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"f6a89abd2d"},{"id":"d33169f972","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）以二十兵团替换九兵团一个军或两个军的部署甚好，但九兵团的主力仍以作九月战役的第二线兵力（第二梯队）为宜，不要调远了。（二）十三兵团的三十八军、三十九军、四十军应在八月上句调至第一线积极准备九月战役，而从三兵团及十九兵团中抽出三至四个军接替海防兵力。（三）在最前线修建多数粮弹储备库，为九月战役储备充分的粮弹，使作战时能随缺随补，此点极关重要。闻你已在筹备，未知情形怎样。（四）以上各点盼复。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"f6a89abd2d"},{"id":"59a52a83c5","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"f6a89abd2d"},{"id":"772564c01d","type":"paragraph","text":"八月一日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"f6a89abd2d"}],"page":{"id":"8983c57fe4","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"f6a89abd2d","start":464,"end":464}}}},"__N_SSG":true}